&lt;p&gt;Constantijn: thanks for this suggestion.  The one significant change i made from your original files (BTW: a patch would have been much easier to review) is that i made the &quot;rootName&quot; option completely replace the previous default: &quot;solr/&quot; + coreName (as opposed to your version where only the &quot;solr&quot; literal was was replaced by the rootName)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Since this lives in solrconfig.xml it&apos;s a core specific setting, and core properties can be used to include the coreName in the rootName if that&apos;s what people desire&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
